<DOCUMENT source-infobase-name="Rules" content-collection-id="NYCrules" source-infobase-title="The Rules of the City of New York" base-output-dir="D:\process\NFOProcess\codes\ny\newyorkcity\NYCrules\output\HUCCVLERTKEUARDR\" default-split-level="Chapter" makefile-filename="D:\process\NFOProcess\codes\ny\newyorkcity\NYCrules\output\HUCCVLERTKEUARDR\NYCrules.mak" css-stylesheet-href="#!-- #ID=NYCrules_css_id --#" xml-output-dir="D:\process\NFOProcess\codes\ny\newyorkcity\NYCrules\output\HUCCVLERTKEUARDR\XML\" css-stylesheet-name="NYCrules_css" makefile-document-depth="2">
	<LEVEL style-name="Chapter" style-name-escaped="Chapter" style-id="0-0-0-477" level-depth="2" toc-section="false">
		<RECORD id="0-0-0-154909" number="67306" version="3014">
			<HEADING>Chapter 47: Rules Pertaining to Recurring Violations and Complaint-Based Inspections</HEADING>
			<PARA>
				<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-8221" name="T28C047"/>Chapter 47: Rules Pertaining to Recurring Violations and Complaint-Based Inspections</PARA>
		</RECORD>
		<LEVEL style-name="Subchapter" style-name-escaped="Subchapter" style-id="0-0-0-480" level-depth="3" toc-section="false">
			<LEVEL style-name="Subtitle" style-name-escaped="Subtitle" style-id="0-0-0-15301" level-depth="4" toc-section="false">
				<LEVEL style-name="Part" style-name-escaped="Part" style-id="0-0-0-483" level-depth="5" toc-section="false">
					<LEVEL style-name="Subpart" style-name-escaped="Subpart" style-id="0-0-0-15960" level-depth="6" toc-section="false">
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-109844" number="67307" version="2306">
								<HEADING>§ 47-01 [Recurring Violations and Complaint-Based Inspections.]</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-8223" name="T28C047_47-01"/>§ 47-01 [Recurring Violations and Complaint-Based Inspections.]</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-59320" number="67308" version="1867">
									<PARA>A complaint-based inspection shall not be subject to the complaint-based inspection fee and shall not be included in the total number of such inspections within a twelve-month period that qualifies a dwelling unit for the complaint-based inspection fee authorized by Administrative Code § <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="27-2115" destination-id="0-0-0-0">27-2115</LINK>(f)(8) where such inspection results exclusively in the issuance of an immediately hazardous or hazardous violation for only one or more of the following conditions: <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-001]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-59321" number="67309" version="3">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(a)<TAB tab-count="1"/>inoperable or missing smoke detector; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-001]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-59322" number="67310" version="3">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(b)<TAB tab-count="1"/>inoperable or missing carbon monoxide detector; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-001]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-59323" number="67311" version="3">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(c)<TAB tab-count="1"/>double cylinder lock on entry door of the dwelling unit; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-001]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-59324" number="67312" version="3">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(d)<TAB tab-count="1"/>illegal window gate; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-001]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-59325" number="67313" version="3">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(e)<TAB tab-count="1"/>improper installation or absence of a window guard; or <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-001]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-59326" number="67314" version="3">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(f)<TAB tab-count="1"/>failure to maintain a dwelling unit in a clean and sanitary condition, including, but not limited to, an accumulation of refuse/rubbish. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-001]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-59327" number="67315" version="55">
									<PARA>(Added City Record 7/21/2015, eff. 8/20/2015) <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-001]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-59328" number="67316" version="1167">
								<HEADING>§ 47-02 [Objections.]</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-8225" name="T28C047_47-02"/>§ 47-02 [Objections.]</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-59329" number="67317" version="2306">
									<PARA>An owner may object, pursuant to Administrative Code § <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="27-2129" destination-id="0-0-0-0">27-2129</LINK>, to the imposition of the complaint-based inspection fee authorized by Administrative Code § <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="27-2115" destination-id="0-0-0-0">27-2115</LINK>(f)(8). An owner may object on the basis that he or she has attempted and failed to gain access to make repairs to the dwelling unit that is the subject of this fee. Such objection shall be made pursuant to Article 8 of Subchapter 5 of <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="T27C002" destination-id="0-0-0-0">Chapter 2 of Title 27</LINK> of the Administrative Code, and the rules promulgated thereunder in 28 RCNY <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Jump" destination-name="T28C017" destination-id="0-0-0-7683">Chapter 17</LINK>. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-001]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-59330" number="67318" version="55">
									<PARA>(Added City Record 7/21/2015, eff. 8/20/2015) <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-001]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
					</LEVEL>
				</LEVEL>
			</LEVEL>
		</LEVEL>
	</LEVEL>
</DOCUMENT>